<% if test.success? %>
  An alert was issued for incoming data from the ODK Aggregate server
  <%= form.server.name %> at <%= form.server.url %>. A submission for the form
  <%= form.form_id %> triggered an alert with this message:

  <%= alert.message %>
<% else %>
  An alert issued an error for incoming data from the ODK Aggregate server
  <%= form.server.name %> at <%= form.server.url %>. A submission for the form
  <%= form.form_id %> could not be processed for the following reason:

  <%= test.error %>

  To view or edit the alert, visit:

  <%= edit_data_source_alert_url(data_source, alert) %>
<% end %>
